#       chạy script pwsh xuống mỗi host qua quickwin.dev/winrsexec (WinRM cert-auth,
#       -EncodedCommand). AppFactory: dispatch AppWinRS → WinRSApp. api/projects/inventory.go:
#       Add/UpdateInventory chấp nhận type "winrs" (nếu thiếu → API từ chối tạo inventory).
#       UI: "WinRS Endpoints" vào dropdown NEW INVENTORY + editor host (cert), app "WinRS".
#       go.mod: require quickwin.dev/winrsexec (replace ../winrs-exec).
# SPEC: docs/L2-specs/core-patches/0009-winrs-app.md
# BASELINE: v2.18.16
#
